highlights.text: “Tu Aake Dekhle” by King has been on Top Songs Guwahati the longest, at 55 weeks straight.
Pritam has the most spots on Top Songs Guwahati. “Kesariya” is the highest at #1.
“Tera Hone Laga Hoon” by Atif Aslam, Alisha Chinai, and Pritam is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Guwahati, up 40 spots at #57.
“Khudaya Khair” by Imdad Hussain and RDRKSH is the highest new entry on Top Songs Guwahati at #62.
